subject: Olympic Games (2012)
Track and Field
lead_paragraph: In the final event of Monday’s United States Track and Field trials, Nick Symmonds broke from the pack of the final lap of the 800-meter run and brought the crowd to its feet, winning in 1 minute 43.92 seconds.
